# This gitignore is a whitelist. Inspired by https://rgbcu.be/blog/gitignore

*

!.gitignore
!.golangci.yml

# Track only repo-owned root docs, prompts, and instructions; future scratch notes stay ignored by default.
!AGENTS.md
!.github/
!.github/**/*
!docs/
!docs/**/*
!LICENSE.md
!README.md

# Root-level Go sources and tests stay explicit; local scratch and gate outputs remain ignored by default.
!*.go
!searchDeciderPrompt.txt
!cmd/
!cmd/**/*
# Keep repo-owned YAML files explicit; local runtime config stays ignored by default.

# Keep runtime and deployment manifests explicit so local-only config files remain ignored.
# In particular, `config-example.yaml` is tracked while user-specific `config.yaml` stays ignored.
!Dockerfile
!config-example.yaml
!docker-compose.yaml
!go.mod
!go.sum
!render.yaml
